{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"149-timmy-and-pepe","title":"Timmy and Pepe","description":"Come, listen to Timmy and Pepe talk to each other. Do you also like to talk to your pet?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Madhav Chavan"],"illustrators":["Santosh Pujari"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/149-timmy-and-pepe"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/701010/size3/e47e8431f29c226becbf3dc0b7a82b99.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/701010/size6/e47e8431f29c226becbf3dc0b7a82b99.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1782/size6/377bc6b20b436d447f1f1018c336332a.jpg","text":"I am Timmy.\nThis is my friend, Pepe, the puppy.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1783/size6/e2231a7ad37808abb79a04610ab5b902.jpg","text":"I like to tease Pepe.\nI tell him I am better than him.\nHe does not like it.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1784/size6/0c58c9f24a9fd3c590f319f256fcf31c.jpg","text":"“Look, I have a nose!” I say.\n“Woof,” says Pepe. That means he has a nose too.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1785/size6/8ba42ecc9459669833a80646c41b05b0.jpg","text":"“Look, I have ears!” I say.\n“Woof,” says Pepe. That means he has ears too.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1786/size6/dcfbd94aa971d9595ab9e4f4efbb93d2.jpg","text":"“Look, I have eyes!” I say.\n“Woof,” says Pepe. That means he has eyes too.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1787/size6/b9ffaf7b06aacf81dd1ace53bdce15dc.jpg","text":"“Look, I can dance on my legs!” I say.\n“Woof, woof, woof,” says Pepe. That means he has legs too.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1788/size6/337644e1478e9fdc5d8c32932ff72737.jpg","text":"“Look, I have a tongue!” I say.\n“Woof,” says Pepe. That means he has a tongue too.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1789/size6/3df93b1ae96c52a3b04d56091a340ffc.jpg","text":"“I can think!” I say.\n“Wooooooof,” says Pepe. That means he can think better.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1790/size6/7654388466ab3e65647d3b305acdd52a.jpg","text":"“Look I have hands!” I say.\n“Grrrrrr…” Pepe says, and turns to show his little tail.\nThat means he has a tail and I don’t have one.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1791/size6/d7dca29ed29aa813a46b77a855ad1496.jpg","text":"But I love Pepe, the puppy and he loves me too.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/1792/size6/b9e66ff673206805cfb8288ec31ab552.jpg","text":"In the picture above find:\nEyes        Hands        Nose       Legs       Tongue       Ears","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":175}}